LFMM GUI to compile version 1.2, 05/24/13
by Eric Frichot (efrichot@gmail.com or eric.frichot@imag.fr)

*******************
*   INSTALLATION   *
*******************
R is mandatory to display Manhattan plot.

1. Just double-click on LFMM_GUI.install 

2. Double-click on LFMM_GUI in LFMM main directory.

******************
*  ORGANIZATION  *
******************

It is organized in 4 folders:
- code
- documentation
- examples
- scripts


PLEASE, read the documentation before using our software. It provides
examples and information on the model and the software.

PLEASE, if you find a bug, contact us. We will fix it as soon as possible.

**************
*  VERSIONS  *
**************

1.1: 	- First main version

1.2: 	- Bug fixed on the transformation of zscore in p-values.
	- Windows version is not multithreaded.
	- Windows GUI is a bit faster.
